or their own local archives.  The server products use the ADDE

protocol.  The local archives are based on the GEMPAK NWX tables.

For the latter, you must have GEMPAK installed and have the

appropriate environment variables defined for the NWX program.

</div>

<p><hr align="center" width="10%"><p><a name="TARGET_ReleaseNotes__atcfalpha12"></a><div class="faq-question"><h4>  ATCF Tropical Storm track display</h4></div>
</a>

<div class="faq-answer"><b> </b> 

