    <br>

    <strong><sup>(4)</sup></strong>You must have DirectX version 8.0+ installed on your Windows system if you use the Direct-X rendering mode of Java 3D (the default is to use OpenGL).

    <br>

<a name="TARGET_Systems__java" id="java"></a>
</blockquote>

