<li><a href="#TARGET_EumetcastHritChooser__FILE">Choosing Eumetcast HRIT Data</a></li>
</ul>



<br>

<hr style="page-break-after: always;">
<a name="TARGET_FileChooser__FILE">
<div class="pagetitle">Choosing Data on Disk</div>

<p>The <strong>General-&gt;Files/Directories</strong> chooser allows you to select

  data or a directory from your file system. For more information on using this

chooser, see <a href="#TARGET_LocalFiles__FILE">Getting
  Started</a>.</p>

