<a name="TARGET_UrlChooser__FILE">
<div class="pagetitle">Choosing a URL</div>

<p>The <strong>General-&gt;URLs</strong> chooser allows you to specify the internet location (URL) of a data source. This URL may be a web page, a bundle or any data file that McIDAS-V can process from a URL. For more information on using this chooser, see <a href="#TARGET_UrlFiles__FILE">Getting Started</a>.</p>
<a name="TARGET_UrlChooser__image1" id="image1"></a>
<div class="cimg"><img src="data/choosers/images/UrlChooser.gif" alt="URL Chooser">
<br>

<span class="caption">Image 1: URL Chooser</span></div>

<div class="pagesubtitle">Properties</div>

<ul>

