<li style="list-style: none">If left as "I'm Feeling Lucky", McIDAS-V will figure out what kind of data is in the file by the URL itself. This can be overridden by selecting the type of data the file contains from the pull down menu. Click <a href="#TARGET_DataSources__FILE">here</a> for a list of available data source types.</li>
<li><strong>URL:</strong></li>

