<a name="TARGET_ImageChooser__FILE">
<div class="pagetitle">Choosing Satellite Imagery</div>

<p>The <strong>Satellite Imagery</strong> chooser allows you to access satellite imagery on remote ADDE servers. For more information on how to use this chooser, see <a href="#TARGET_Satellite__FILE">Getting Started</a>.</p>
<a name="TARGET_ImageChooser__image1" id="image1"></a>
<div class="cimg"><img src="data/choosers/images/ImageChooser.gif" alt="Image Chooser">
