<li style="list-style: none">Allows you to choose one or more absolute times. When choosing absolute times for the first time McIDAS-V needs to query the ADDE server for the times. This may take some time. To select more than one time use Control-Click or Shift-Click. See the <a href="#TARGET_Timeline__FILE">Timeline section</a> for details on its use. Click on the <img src="data/choosers/images/SelectDay.gif" width="16" height="16"> <strong>Select Archive Day</strong> to narrow down a large dataset to one day.</li>
