<div class="pagesubtitle">Image Properties</div>

<p>The image properties section allows you to override the default properties

  McIDAS-V uses to specify other aspects of the image data. The widgets show

  the defaults McIDAS-V will use. By changing any of the widgets you can override

  the default value. Currently, there is a chooser under development with

  the image properties moved to the <strong>Field Selector</strong>, along with

  a new geolocation selector box with an image preview. This chooser can be viewed

    by selecting <strong>Under

    Development -&gt; Satellite Imagery</strong> from the list of choosers in

  the <strong>Data Explorer</strong>.</p>

<ul>

<li><strong>Data Type:</strong></li>

<li style="list-style: none">Change the data type to be displayed.</li>

<li><strong>Channel:</strong></li>

<li style="list-style: none">Change the channel to be displayed.</li>

<li><strong>Location:</strong></li>

<li style="list-style: none">Use the <img src="data/choosers/images/Toggle.gif" width="16" height="18"> toggle button to specify the placement point of the image at either the center or the upper left.</li>
<li><strong>Lat:/Lon:</strong></li>

<li style="list-style: none">Enter in a latitude and longitude to center the image on. Click on the <img src="data/choosers/images/Toggle.gif" width="16" height="18"> <strong>toggle</strong> button to switch to Line/Element.</li>
<li><strong>Line:/Element:</strong></li>

<li style="list-style: none">Enter in a line and element to center the image on. Click on the <img src="data/choosers/images/Toggle.gif" width="16" height="18"> <strong>toggle</strong> button to switch to Latitude/Longitude.</li>
<li><img src="data/choosers/images/CenterDisplay.gif" width="18" height="18"> <strong>Center Display</strong></li>
<li style="list-style: none">Click to center the image over the center, upper left, upper right, lower left, or lower right latitude and longitude coordinates of the of the current main display.</li>

<li><strong>Image Size:</strong></li>

<li style="list-style: none">Change the size of the image.</li>

<li><img src="data/choosers/images/Lock.gif" width="9" height="12"> <strong>Lock - Locked</strong></li>
<li style="list-style: none">When the <strong>Image Size</strong> is locked, changing the magnification will have no effect on the image size.</li>

<li><img src="data/choosers/images/Unlock.gif" width="12" height="12"> <strong>Lock - Unlocked</strong></li>
<li style="list-style: none">When the <strong>Image Size</strong> is unlocked, changing the magnification will change the image size accordingly.</li>

<li><strong>Magnification:</strong></li>

<li style="list-style: none">Use the <img src="data/choosers/images/Slider.gif" width="18" height="12"> sliders to change the magnification of the image.</li>
<li><strong>Navigation Type:</strong></li>

<li style="list-style: none">Use the pull down menu to select the default navigation, or to choose to use Lat/Lon navigation.</li>

</ul>

