</li>

<a name="TARGET_DisplayMenus__goto"></a>
<li><code class="menu">Go to Address</code></li>

<li style="list-style: none">

<div class="menudesc">Change the projection to a given address, zip code, city, etc.

<div class="cimg"><img src="ui/images/Address.gif" alt="images/Address.gif"></div>
The formats include:

<pre>

12345 oak street, my town, my state

my town, my state

80303 (zip code)

latitude longitude

