<br>

<strong>Shift-Right Mouse Drag:</strong> Hold <strong>Shift</strong> key and drag the right mouse button (MB3). Moving up zooms in, moving down zooms out.</td>

<td><strong>Control-Right Mouse Drag:</strong> Hold <strong>Control</strong> key and drag right mouse to pan.</td>

