McIDAS-V can display QuickTime movies. You can pause, single step and play a

movie.

<div class="cimg"><img src="controls/misc/images/QuickTimeControlGui.gif"  alt="images/QuickTimeControlGui.gif" ></div>
<div class="pagesubtitle">Properties</div>

<ul>

<li><strong><img src="controls/misc/images/play.gif" width="17" height="21"> Play</strong></li>
  <p>Click to start the QuickTime movie.</p>

  <p></p>

<li><strong><img src="controls/misc/images/pause.gif" width="17" height="21"> Pause</strong></li>
  <p>Click to pause the QuickTime movie.</p>

  <p></p>

<li><strong><img src="controls/misc/images/backstep.gif" width="17" height="21"> Step Backward</strong></li>
  <p>Click to move backwards a single step in the movie.</p>

  <p></p>

<li><strong><img src="controls/misc/images/forwardstep.gif" width="17" height="21"> Step
      Forward</strong></li>

  <p>Click to move forwards a single step in the movie.</p>

  <p></p>

<li><strong><img src="controls/misc/images/quicktimeproperties.gif" width="17" height="21"> Media
      Properties </strong></li>

  <p>Left-click to bring up the QuickTime media properties.  Right-click to change

