<div class="pagesubsubtitle">&lt;<a name="TARGET_DataAndDisplays__reload" id="reload"></a><em>reload</em>&gt; Reload all loaded data</div>
The <em>reload</em> tag tells all of the loaded data sources to reload, resulting in updated displays.

<blockquote>

<pre>

