<a name="TARGET_3DSurface__2dtopo" id="2dtopo"></a>
<div class="pagesubtitle">2D Data Draped Over Topography</div>

<p>Two dimensional grid data can be draped over a topography field to provide a terrain following representation of the data.</p>

<a name="TARGET_3DSurface__image5" id="image5"></a>
<div class="cimg"><img src="examples/images/PressureOverTopography.gif" alt="Sea level pressure over topography">
